      "name": "GhostPairing Lookalike Domains",
      "description": "A set of domains used in GhostPairing attacks to host fake Facebook-style viewer pages. Examples include photobox[.]life, postsphoto[.]life, yourphoto[.]life, photopost[.]live, yourphoto[.]world, top-foto[.]life, and fotoface[.]top. These domains proxy pairing requests and display lure messages.",
